      <title>termux菜蛋</title>
      <link href="/year/02/05/termux%E8%8F%9C%E8%9B%8B/"/>
      <url>/year/02/05/termux%E8%8F%9C%E8%9B%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一、彩虹猫</p><ol><li></li></ol> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg i nyancat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li></li></ol> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nyancat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>二、代码雨</p><ol><li></li></ol> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt i cmatrix</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li></li></ol> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cmatrix</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>三、小火车</p><ol><li></li></ol> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt update &amp;&amp; apt upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li></li></ol> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt i sl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li></li></ol> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
