      <title>termux内网穿透教程</title>
      <link href="/year/01/25/Termux%E5%86%85%E7%BD%91%E7%A9%BF%E9%80%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/year/01/25/Termux%E5%86%85%E7%BD%91%E7%A9%BF%E9%80%8F%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一、先去樱花内网穿透官网注册账户</p><p>注册完成后创建隧道</p><p>并复制你的密钥</p><p>樱花内网穿透官网链接：<a href="https://www.natfrp.com"实名需一元"/">点击前往</a></p><hr><p>二、打开termux输入</p> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   pkg install proot</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">termux-chroot</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">curl -L -o frp https://getfrp.sh/d/frpc_linux_arm64</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">chmod +x frp</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">./frp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>三、输入.&#x2F;frp后会弹出一个对话框，在对话框中点击蓝色输入框，输入你刚才复制的密钥。</p><p>按回车键选择并确认你创建的隧道<br>按<code>ctrl+c</code>来开启隧道<br>关闭隧道也按<code>ctrl+c</code><br><img src="https://www.helloimg.com/images/2023/02/21/oPCaJq.jpg"></p>]]></content>
      
      
